  "text": "All imaging data and analyses, at the 24-h time point, are new and have not been previously published. The imaging study during the infusion day is a novel connectivity analysis of a previously published pharmaco-MRI data set. [CITATION_1] None of the reported connectivity measures and analyses in the current report overlap with the previous study. The details of the clinical trial and the behavioral effects of the study drugs have been reported previously [CITATION_2] and are not included in the current paper.",
